Interface BoolPred

All Known Subinterfaces:
pBoolPred
All Known Implementing Classes:
Cond, False, True
public interface BoolPred

An implementation of Boolean Predicates using BDDs. The functions which take arguments of type BoolPred may throw a ClassCastException if given an object that was not created by BoolPred.factory().
